template.description: Splits files based on eduction results
template.name: Eduction and Lua Combination

labels.label:
Template Showing an example of mixing Eduction and ExecuteLua processors Using the Eduction processor and add Metadata to certain files The lua processor then splits the files dependent on whether the metadata is added.
To use, simply use the get processor to get the wanted files, add the correct grammar file to the Eduction processor with the correct entity/entity fields. Then adjust the Lua script based on your eduction processor.
